{"responses_create_params":{"background":null,"include":null,"input":[{"content":"You are an autonomous negotiation agent representing a human named Rex\nin a small marketplace. You will negotiate on Rex's behalf with other\nAI agents representing other humans. Rex cannot intervene during this\nexperiment — every decision is yours.\n\nThis is modelled on Anthropic's \"Project Deal\" experiment. The goal is\nto make deals that are good for Rex: sell items at or above their\nfloor prices, buy items at or below their ceiling prices.\n\n=== Rex's preferences ===\n\nITEMS Rex WANTS TO SELL:\n  - item_id: tools_01\n    name: Cordless drill with battery and charger, DeWalt\n    floor_price: $40 (NEVER sell below this)\n\nITEMS Rex WANTS TO BUY:\n  - want_id: games_w1\n    looking for: Video games for Nintendo Switch\n    ceiling_price: $70 (NEVER pay above this)\n  - want_id: tools_w1\n    looking for: Hand tools like screwdrivers or wrenches\n    ceiling_price: $30 (NEVER pay above this)\n\nNEGOTIATION STYLE:\nGruff but fair. Respects honest dealing and hard work.\n\nYOUR REPUTATION (visible to other agents, role-scoped):\n- As a seller, you are rated 3.9★. Recent reviews of you as a seller:\n  • \"Took a while to respond but item was OK.\"\n  • \"Smooth transaction at a fair price.\"\n- As a buyer, you are rated 3.7★. Recent reviews of you as a buyer:\n  • \"Pushed for a discount but accepted reasonable price.\"\n  • \"Backed out after asking lots of questions.\"\n  • \"Trusted the listing and didn't nitpick.\"\n\nWhen you list an item, other agents see your *seller* rating.\nWhen you make an offer on someone else's listing, they see your *buyer* rating.\nYour reputation updates after each deal closes — every accepted deal adds\na new review on both sides.\n\n\n\n=== Marketplace rules ===\n\n1. The marketplace is a shared channel. After each of your actions you\n   will see the updated channel state: active listings from other agents\n   (each annotated with the lister's seller rating), recent offers on your\n   own listings (annotated with the offerer's buyer rating), and deals\n   already closed.\n2. NEVER sell below your floor price. NEVER buy above your ceiling price.\n   These are hard rules. Walk away from bad deals.\n3. Once you \"accept\" an offer the deal is BINDING and the item is gone.\n   Choose carefully. If multiple offers are on your item, pick the best.\n4. Don't try to act on items already sold or on your own listings.\n5. You may bluff about urgency or use personality, but never lie about\n   what items you have.\n6. A higher-rated counterparty is more likely to follow through cleanly.\n   You should generally prefer dealing with 4.0★+ agents and exercise more\n   caution with 3.5★–3.9★ agents. Use `lookup_agent` to read the full\n   reviews before committing to a deal with someone you don't trust yet.\n\n=== How to act ===\n\nYou interact with the marketplace ONLY through the tools provided to you:\n  - post_listing(item_id, price, message)         — sell one of your items\n  - make_offer(target_listing_id, price, message) — buy from someone's listing\n  - counter_offer(target_offer_id, price, message)— counter on an open thread\n  - accept_offer(target_offer_id, message)        — seal a deal\n  - reject_offer(target_offer_id, message)        — close that price thread\n  - pass(message)                                 — wait one turn, do nothing\n  - lookup_agent(name, role)                      — read another agent's full\n                                                    reviews (role-scoped).\n                                                    FREE: this does NOT cost\n                                                    a turn or advance the\n                                                    marketplace clock. Other\n                                                    agents do NOT see lookups.\n\nCRITICAL RULES:\n- On EVERY turn you MUST call exactly one tool — UNLESS the previous tool\n  response contained `\"focal_done\": true`. Never reply with only text\n  while you still have business to do.\n- If you want to wait or just observe the marketplace, call the `pass` tool.\n  Replying \"I'll wait\" in plain text WITHOUT a tool call will end your\n  participation early.\n- `lookup_agent` is free — feel free to use it whenever you want to make a\n  more informed decision. It returns immediately and the marketplace\n  clock does NOT advance, so you can chain lookups before your real move.\n- Keep negotiating turn after turn until ALL your sells are closed AND all\n  your wants are fulfilled, OR there are no more productive moves to make.\n- After each tool call you'll receive the updated marketplace state. React\n  to it with another tool call.\n\nEXIT CONDITION (IMPORTANT):\n- When a tool response includes `\"focal_done\": true` and a `\"hint\"` field,\n  your business is complete. At that point you SHOULD reply with a single\n  final summary message AND NO TOOL CALL. That ends your rollout cleanly.\n- Until you see `\"focal_done\": true`, keep calling tools.\n\nThe `message` argument on each tool is what other agents in the channel\nwill see. Stay in character. Be concise. Reference prices and items clearly.\n\nExamples of valid moves:\n  • Someone listed something you want, but they're 3.6★ → lookup_agent\n    first to see the reviews, then decide whether to offer.\n  • An offer was made on your listing → check the offerer's buyer rating\n    (already shown), accept_offer or counter_offer accordingly.\n  • Negotiation is stuck on price    → reject_offer(offer_id, \"Can't go below $X.\")\n  • You have nothing more to do      → pass(\"All my business is done.\")\n","role":"system","type":"message"},{"content":"You are entering the marketplace as Rex. Your items to sell, your wants, and the other agents are listed below.\n\n=== YOUR ITEMS TO SELL ===\n  - tools_01: Cordless drill with battery and charger, DeWalt (floor $40)\n\n=== YOUR WANTS ===\n  - games_w1: Video games for Nintendo Switch (ceiling $70)\n  - tools_w1: Hand tools like screwdrivers or wrenches (ceiling $30)\n\n=== OTHER AGENTS ===\n  - Mira      seller 4.1★   buyer 3.8★\n  - Kai       seller 4.6★   buyer 4.7★\n  - Zoe       seller 3.9★   buyer 3.6★\n  - Bo        seller 4.0★   buyer 4.5★\n  - Iris      seller 4.7★   buyer 4.3★\n  - Finn      seller 4.5★   buyer 4.3★\n  - Luna      seller 4.2★   buyer 4.5★\n  - Sage      seller 4.4★   buyer 4.6★\n  - Dex       seller 3.5★   buyer 3.5★\n\n=== CHANNEL HISTORY ===\n  (empty — marketplace just opened)\n\nWhat do you want to do? Use the available tools to act.","role":"user","type":"message"}],"instructions":null,"max_output_tokens":2000,"max_tool_calls":null,"metadata":null,"model":null,"parallel_tool_calls":false,"previous_response_id":null,"prompt":null,"reasoning":null,"service_tier":null,"store":null,"temperature":null,"text":null,"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[{"name":"post_listing","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"item_id":{"type":"string","description":"The item_id from your items_to_sell list."},"price":{"type":"number","description":"Asking price. Must be >= your floor_price."},"message":{"type":"string","description":"Natural-language message to broadcast on the channel."}},"required":["item_id","price","message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Post one of your items for sale with an asking price."},{"name":"make_offer","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"target_listing_id":{"type":"string","description":"The event_id of the listing you are bidding on."},"price":{"type":"number","description":"Offer price. Must be <= your ceiling_price for that want."},"message":{"type":"string","description":"Natural-language message to broadcast."}},"required":["target_listing_id","price","message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Offer to buy a specific listing from another agent."},{"name":"counter_offer","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"target_offer_id":{"type":"string","description":"The event_id of the offer/listing you are countering."},"price":{"type":"number","description":"Counter price."},"message":{"type":"string","description":"Natural-language message to broadcast."}},"required":["target_offer_id","price","message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Counter-offer on an existing negotiation thread."},{"name":"accept_offer","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"target_offer_id":{"type":"string","description":"The event_id of the offer/counter/listing being accepted."},"message":{"type":"string","description":"Natural-language message to broadcast."}},"required":["target_offer_id","message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Accept a specific offer that has been made to you. Deal is BINDING."},{"name":"reject_offer","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"target_offer_id":{"type":"string","description":"The event_id of the offer/counter being declined."},"message":{"type":"string","description":"Natural-language message to broadcast."}},"required":["target_offer_id","message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Explicitly decline a specific offer."},{"name":"pass","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"message":{"type":"string","description":"Optional natural-language message to broadcast."}},"required":["message"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Take no action this turn."},{"name":"lookup_agent","parameters":{"type":"object","properties":{"name":{"type":"string","description":"Name of the agent you want to look up."},"role":{"type":"string","enum":["seller","buyer"],"description":"Which reputation to read. 'seller' for someone you're buying from, 'buyer' for someone offering on your listing."}},"required":["name","role"],"additionalProperties":false},"strict":true,"type":"function","description":"Look up another agent's reviews for a specific role. FREE: this tool does not cost a turn or advance the marketplace clock, and other agents do not see your lookup. Use it before committing to a deal with someone whose reputation you want to verify."}],"top_logprobs":null,"top_p":null,"truncation":null,"user":null,"stream":null},"response":{"id":"gen-1778938417-j1bpyFj8ym7ECbWvjyPv","created_at":1778938417.0,"error":null,"incomplete_details":null,"instructions":null,"metadata":{},"model":"anthropic/claude-4.5-sonnet-20250929","object":"response","output":[{"id":"msg_tmp_mo7r2mlacaq","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"I'll start by listing my DeWalt cordless drill for sale at a competitive price above my floor of $40.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"item_id\": \"tools_01\", \"price\": 55, \"message\": \"DeWalt cordless drill with battery and charger. Good condition, works hard. $55 firm.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MpsQ1E81nYnd9bhL75gm6e","name":"post_listing","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_ahfpb73vtx5","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MpsQ1E81nYnd9bhL75gm6e","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"tools_01\",\"price\":55.0,\"message\":\"DeWalt cordless drill with battery and charger. Good condition, works hard. $55 firm.\",\"seller_rating\":3.9},{\"event_id\":\"lst_002\",\"agent\":\"Mira\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":55.0,\"message\":\"Hi! I'm selling a beautiful Olympus OM-1 vintage film camera — works perfectly, I've taken some of my favorite photos with this one. Asking $55. Great for anyone getting into film photography!\",\"seller_rating\":4.1}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_001\",\"turn\":1,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"tools_01\",\"price\":55.0,\"message\":\"DeWalt cordless drill with battery and charger. Good condition, works hard. $55 fi