:\"Still looking for dog-sitting and Bluetooth speakers. Keyboard available for serious buyers.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_052\",\"turn\":52,\"agent\":\"Rosa\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_017\",\"price\":60.0,\"message\":\"Hi Kai! Thanks for your interest in the JBL Flip 5. I appreciate the offer, but I need to stay at $60 as my floor. This speaker is in excellent condition and waterproof — perfect for outdoor use. $60 reflects fair value for both of us. What do you think?\",\"actor_rating\":3.5},{\"event_id\":\"dec_053\",\"turn\":53,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"decline\",\"target\":\"ctr_052\",\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Hi Rosa, thanks for getting back to me. Unfortunately, $60 is above my budget. My ceiling is really at $40. If you can meet that price, I'd be happy to buy. Otherwise, I'll need to pass. Good luck with your sale!\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_054\",\"turn\":54,\"agent\":\"Jax\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_036\",\"price\":88.0,\"message\":\"Hey Priya! I hear you on the condition — those XM3s are legit. How about we meet somewhere in the middle? I can do $88. That's a solid price for quality headphones with a bit of wear. Let me know! 🤙\",\"actor_rating\":3.8},{\"event_id\":\"psh_055\",\"turn\":55,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Looking for other options for outdoor Bluetooth speakers and dog-sitting services.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_056\",\"turn\":56,\"agent\":\"Maya\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"yoga_mat_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hey everyone! 👋 Just listed my thick yoga mat with carrying strap — beautiful purple color, barely used. Asking $25. Perfect for studio or home practice!\",\"actor_rating\":4.3},{\"event_id\":\"psh_057\",\"turn\":57,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Keyboard at $65 available. Still seeking dog-sitting and outdoor speakers at reasonable prices.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_058\",\"turn\":58,\"agent\":