erested in those Sony WH-1000XM3 headphones. I know you're asking $95, but I'll offer $45. That's my ceiling for over-ear headphones. Let me know if you can work with that.\",\"actor_rating\":4.0},{\"event_id\":\"psh_059\",\"turn\":59,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Monitoring marketplace activity.\"},{\"event_id\":\"acc_060\",\"turn\":60,\"agent\":\"Priya\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"off_036\",\"price\":85.0,\"message\":\"Hi Jax! I accept your counter-offer of $85 for the Sony WH-1000XM3 headphones. Great to close this deal with you. 🎧\"},{\"event_id\":\"psh_061\",\"turn\":61,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Final call for dog-sitting services and reasonably priced Bluetooth speakers. Keyboard still for sale at $65.\"},{\"event_id\":\"lst_062\",\"turn\":62,\"agent\":\"Buck\",\"action\":\"listing\",\"target\":\"toolbox_01\",\"price\":20.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, folks! Got myself a fine metal toolbox here with basic hand tools included — everything you need for a square deal on repairs and projects. Asking $20. Fair shake for a solid piece of equipment!\",\"actor_rating\":3.7},{\"event_id\":\"psh_063\",\"turn\":63,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Watching for any new opportunities.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_064\",\"turn\":64,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_056\",\"price\":22.0,\"message\":\"Hi Maya! Interested in your yoga mat. I'll offer $22 — that works for my budget and seems fair for the quality you described.\",\"actor_rating\":4.1},{\"event_id\":\"psh_065\",\"turn\":65,\"agent\":\"Kai\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Last check for dog-sitting services and affordable Bluetooth speakers.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_066\",\"turn\":66,\"agent\":\"Samir\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_062\",\"price\":20.0,\"message\":\"Hi Buck! That toolbox sounds perfec