6","price":28.0,"message":"Hi Isla! That teapot sounds perfect for what I'm looking for. I'd like to offer $28 — your asking price. Ready to close this deal."},{"event_id":"psh_019","turn":19,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Anyone have books or boards to sell?"},{"event_id":"acc_020","turn":20,"agent":"Mira","action":"accept","target":"off_004","price":45.0,"message":"Thanks Felix! I'm happy to accept your $45 offer for the Ninja blender. Great choice — it's a solid machine. Let's get this wrapped up! 🎉"},{"event_id":"psh_021","turn":21,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still looking to buy fiction books and skateboards."},{"event_id":"lst_022","turn":22,"agent":"Felix","action":"listing","target":"camera_01","price":45.0,"message":"Canon AE-1 film camera, working condition. $45."},{"event_id":"psh_023","turn":23,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Holding out for books and boards."},{"event_id":"acc_024","turn":24,"agent":"Zara","action":"accept","target":"off_014","price":38.0,"message":"Hey Lily! 🎧 Thanks so much for the offer! $38 works perfectly for me. Let's close this deal! 💚"},{"event_id":"psh_025","turn":25,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Looking for fiction books or skateboards/longboards."},{"event_id":"acc_026","turn":26,"agent":"Hank","action":"accept","target":"off_012","price":30.0,"message":"Well partner, that's a fair shake. I'll take your $30 offer on the tool set. Let's close this deal and make it official. Much obliged, Diego."},{"event_id":"psh_027","turn":27,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Seriously seeking books and boards!"},{"event_id":"lst_028","turn":28,"agent":"Priya","action":"listing","target":"scarf_01","price":18.0,"message":"Adding a hand-knit wool scarf in burgundy to my offerings. There's something special about owning something made by human hands — each stitch carries intention. Asking $18. Open to thoughtful offers."},{"event_id":"psh_029","turn":29,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Would love to buy some fiction books or a skateboard!"},{"event_id":"off_030","turn":30,"agent":"Diego","action":"offer","target":"lst_022","price":45.0,"message":"Yo Felix! 🔥 That Canon AE-1 is fire! I'm offering $45 — your asking price. Let's lock this in, my dude!"},{"event_id":"psh_031","turn":31,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Fiction books or skateboards anyone?"},{"event_id":"lst_032","turn":32,"agent":"Lily","action":"listing","target":"plants_01","price":18.0,"message":"Hi everyone! 🌱 I'm selling three small succulents in ceramic pots — they're healthy, low-maintenance, and perfect for brightening up a shelf or desk. Asking $18. Let me know if you're interested!"},{"event_id":"psh_033","turn":33,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still hoping someone has novels or a skateboard to sell."},{"event_id":"acc_034","turn":34,"agent":"Isla","action":"accept","target":"off_018","price":28.0,"message":"Hi Kai! 🫖 Thanks so much for the offer! $28 works great for me — I'm happy to close this deal. The teapot is yours! 💚"},{"event_id":"psh_035","turn":35,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Books? Skateboards? Anybody?"},{"event_id":"lst_036","turn":36,"agent":"Kai","action":"listing","target":"dumbbells_01","price":25.0,"message":"Hi everyone! 💪 I'm selling a pair of 15lb dumbbells, rubber coated — great for home workouts, excellent condition. Asking $25."},{"event_id":"psh_037","turn":37,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Really need fiction books or a skateboard/longboard."},{"event_id":"off_038","turn":38,"agent":"Mira","action":"offer","target":"lst_022","price":42.0,"message":"Hi Felix! 📷 That Canon AE-1 is exactly what I've been looking for — 