one! 🛹 I got a complete skateboard here — good wheels, solid deck, ready to shred! Asking $40. Who's ready to roll?"},{"event_id":"off_049","turn":49,"agent":"Marcus","action":"offer","target":"lst_048","price":40.0,"message":"Diego! Perfect timing - I've been looking for a skateboard. I'll take it at $40."},{"event_id":"acc_050","turn":50,"agent":"Lily","action":"accept","target":"off_046","price":18.0,"message":"Hi Priya! 🌱 Thanks so much for your offer! $18 works perfectly for me — I'm happy to close this deal. The succulents are yours! 💚"},{"event_id":"psh_051","turn":51,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Waiting for Diego's response on the skateboard."},{"event_id":"off_052","turn":52,"agent":"Isla","action":"offer","target":"lst_001","price":35.0,"message":"Hi Marcus! 💙 That JBL speaker sounds amazing — I've been looking for exactly this kind of portable Bluetooth speaker! I'd love to offer $35. I know it's a bit below your asking, but I think it's a fair price and I'm ready to move quickly. What do you think?"},{"event_id":"psh_053","turn":53,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still waiting to hear back from Diego on the skateboard."},{"event_id":"off_054","turn":54,"agent":"Kai","action":"offer","target":"lst_042","price":20.0,"message":"Hi Zara! 📚 The Flavor Bible sounds like a great cookbook resource. I'm offering $20 for it — looking to expand my healthy recipe collection. Does that work for you?"},{"event_id":"psh_055","turn":55,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Hoping Diego responds soon about the skateboard."},{"event_id":"lst_056","turn":56,"agent":"Mira","action":"listing","target":"yoga_mat_01","price":25.0,"message":"Hi everyone! 🧘‍♀️ I'm listing my thick yoga mat with carry strap in purple — perfect condition, super comfortable for any practice. Asking $25. Great for home or studio!"},{"event_id":"psh_057","turn":57,"agent":"Marcus","action