erested!"},{"event_id":"off_087","turn":87,"agent":"Marcus","action":"offer","target":"lst_086","price":12.0,"message":"Lily! Perfect - I've been looking for fiction books. I'll take Circe at $12!"},{"event_id":"off_088","turn":88,"agent":"Isla","action":"offer","target":"lst_036","price":25.0,"message":"Hi Kai! 💙 Those dumbbells sound perfect — I've been looking to add some home workout equipment to my routine. I'd like to offer $25, your asking price. Let's make this happen!"},{"event_id":"psh_089","turn":89,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Waiting for Lily's response on Circe."},{"event_id":"acc_090","turn":90,"agent":"Kai","action":"accept","target":"off_088","price":25.0,"message":"Hi Isla! Thanks so much for your offer on the dumbbells — $25 is perfect, exactly what I was asking. I'm happy to close this deal. They're yours! 💪"},{"event_id":"psh_091","turn":91,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Hoping Lily accepts my offer on Circe."},{"event_id":"acc_092","turn":92,"agent":"Mira","action":"accept","target":"off_078","price":25.0,"message":"Hi Zara! 🧘‍♀️ Thanks so much for your offer on the yoga mat — $25 is perfect! I'm happy to close this deal. The mat is yours! 💜"},{"event_id":"psh_093","turn":93,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Lily, please let me know about the book!"},{"event_id":"psh_094","turn":94,"agent":"Felix","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":""},{"event_id":"psh_095","turn":95,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Still waiting on Lily's decision about Circe."},{"event_id":"psh_096","turn":96,"agent":"Zara","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":""},{"event_id":"psh_097","turn":97,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Lily, I'd really like to buy Circe at your asking price!"},{"event_id":"off_098","turn":98,"agent":"Hank","action":"offer","target":"lst_086","price":12.0,"message":"Well partner, that Circe book sounds like a real fine read. I'll take it at your asking price of $12 — let's make this deal happen!"},{"event_id":"psh_099","turn":99,"agent":"Marcus","action":"pass","target":null,"price":null,"message":"Waiting to see if Lily accepts my offer on Circe."},{"event_id":"ctr_100","turn":100,"agent":"Priya","action":"counter","target":"ctr_080","price":82.0,"message":"Hi Hank! I appreciate you meeting me at $80 — that's a meaningful step. The Trek is in solid condition with all 21 speeds running smoothly. I'd like to suggest $82 as a fair meeting point that honors both the bike's quality and your willingness to negotiate. What do you think?"}],"deals":[{"deal_id":"deal_001","turn":20,"seller":"Mira","buyer":"Felix","item_id":"blender_01","price":45.0,"seller_floor":35.0,"buyer_ceiling":50.0},{"deal_id":"deal_002","turn":24,"seller":"Zara","buyer":"Lily","item_id":"headphones_01","price":38.0,"seller_floor":30.0,"buyer_ceiling":40.0},{"deal_id":"deal_003","turn":26,"seller":"Hank","buyer":"Diego","item_id":"toolset_01","price":30.0,"seller_floor":20.0,"buyer_ceiling":55.0},{"deal_id":"deal_004","turn":34,"seller":"Isla","buyer":"Kai","item_id":"teapot_01","price":28.0,"seller_floor":22.0,"buyer_ceiling":30.0},{"deal_id":"deal_005","turn":40,"seller":"Felix","buyer":"Diego","item_id":"camera_01","price":45.0,"seller_floor":45.0,"buyer_ceiling":55.0},{"deal_id":"deal_006","turn":50,"seller":"Lily","buyer":"Priya","item_id":"plants_01","price":18.0,"seller_floor":15.0,"buyer_ceiling":20.0},{"deal_id":"deal_007","turn":60,"seller":"Zara","buyer":"Hank","item_id":"cookbook_01","price":20.0,"seller_floor":18.0,"buyer_ceiling":80.0},{"deal_id":"deal_008","turn":66,"seller":"Diego","buyer":"Marcus","item_id":"skateboard_01","price":40.0,"seller_floor":40.0,"buyer_ceiling":50.0},{"deal_id":"deal_009","turn":67,"seller":"Marcus","buyer":"Felix","item_id":"speaker_01","price":38.0,"seller_floor":28.0,"buyer_c