hanks for the interest in the sci-fi collection! I appreciate the offer, but I need to stay at $25 minimum — these are classic hardcovers in great shape. How does that work for you? 😊\",\"actor_rating\":3.7},{\"event_id\":\"psh_043\",\"turn\":43,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to wait for responses on boots and blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_044\",\"turn\":44,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Taj, appreciate the interest in the boots. They're in fine shape — just some honest wear from ranch work, nothin' that affects the quality. I can come down to $42, but that's my bottom line. Fair deal for solid footwear, partner.\",\"actor_rating\":4.1}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Taj\",\"buyer\":\"Jade\",\"item_id\":\"watch_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"turn\":17},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Kade\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":55.0,\"turn\":20},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":38.0,\"turn\":28},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_004\",\"seller\":\"Rex\",\"buyer\":\"Duke\",\"item_id\":\"drill_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"turn\":30}],\"turn\":44}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_qnufeag8qr","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Excellent! Duke has countered at $42 for the boots. That's $3 below my ceiling of $45, so this is a good deal! Duke has explained the condition is good with only honest wear. Since he's said $42 is his bottom line and it's well within my budget, I should accept this offer.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"target_offer_id\": \"ctr_044\", \"message\": \"Thanks Duke! $42 works perfectly for me. I appreciate you meeting me partway. Looking forward to getting those boots!\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_011vNhdv2LsnucQUudZroBfW",