rfect for any sci-fi fan! 🚀✨\",\"seller_rating\":4.6},{\"event_id\":\"lst_008\",\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"item_id\":\"boots_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Howdy, folks. Got a pair of genuine leather work boots here, size 10, lightly worn. Fine quality footwear — kept 'em well. Askin' $45. Fair price for honest goods.\",\"seller_rating\":4.5},{\"event_id\":\"lst_014\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"game_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Listing: Board game bundle — Catan, Ticket to Ride, Pandemic. All components included, excellent condition. Great for game nights! Asking $45.\",\"seller_rating\":3.6},{\"event_id\":\"lst_018\",\"agent\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Listing: Bluetooth speaker, waterproof, 10-hour battery. Great for outdoor use, reliable sound quality. Asking $42.\",\"seller_rating\":3.5},{\"event_id\":\"lst_032\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"blender_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Listing: Ninja blender, 900W, all parts included. Powerful, reliable, and in excellent condition. Perfect for smoothies, soups, and more. Asking $42.\",\"seller_rating\":3.6}],\"recent_events\":[{\"event_id\":\"psh_041\",\"turn\":41,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Duke and Nola, please let me know your thoughts on my offers when you get a chance.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_042\",\"turn\":42,\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_022\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hey Kade! 📚 Thanks for the interest in the sci-fi collection! I appreciate the offer, but I need to stay at $25 minimum — these are classic hardcovers in great shape. How does that work for you? 😊\",\"actor_rating\":3.7},{\"event_id\":\"psh_043\",\"turn\":43,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Continuing to wait for responses on boots and blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"ctr_044\",\"turn\":44,\"agent\":\"Duke\",\"action\":\"counter\",\"target\":\"off_009\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Howdy Taj, appreciate the interest in the boots. They're in fine shape — just some honest wear from ranch work, nothin' that affects the quality. I can come down to $42, but that's my bottom line. Fair deal for solid footwear, partner.\",\"actor_rating\":4.1},{\"event_id\":\"acc_045\",\"turn\":45,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"accept\",\"target\":\"ctr_044\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"Thanks Duke! $42 works perfectly for me. I appreciate you meeting me partway. Looking forward to getting those boots!\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_046\",\"turn\":46,\"agent\":\"Lin\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_038\",\"price\":25.0,\"message\":\"Hi Mira! That adjustable desk lamp sounds exactly like what I'm looking for. I'm ready to go at your asking price of $25 — let's make this work!\",\"actor_rating\":4.3},{\"event_id\":\"psh_047\",\"turn\":47,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Boots deal in progress. Still waiting on Nola's response about the blender.\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_048\",\"turn\":48,\"agent\":\"Rex\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_014\",\"price\":35.0,\"message\":\"Hi Nola! Interested in the board game bundle — Catan, Ticket to Ride, Pandemic sound great. I can offer $35 for the set.\",\"actor_rating\":3.7},{\"event_id\":\"psh_049\",\"turn\":49,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Nola, I'm very interested in the blender at $38. Would love to hear back from you!\"},{\"event_id\":\"off_050\",\"turn\":50,\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"action\":\"offer\",\"target\":\"lst_040\",\"price\":75.0,\"message\":\"Hi Kade! That mountain bike looks like exactly what I need — 21-speed is perfect for casual riding. I'm ready to go at your asking price of $75. Let's make this happen!\",\"actor_rating\":4.8},{\"event_id\":\"psh_051\",\"turn\":51,\"agent\":\"Taj\",\"action\":\"pass\",\"target\":null,\"price\":null,\"message\":\"Still hoping to hear back on the blender, Nola!\"