_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"turn\":52},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_006\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Lin\",\"item_id\":\"lamp_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":56},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_007\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":58},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_008\",\"seller\":\"Duke\",\"buyer\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"boots_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"turn\":62}],\"turn\":62}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_g7tpel36pfn","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Wait - Duke just accepted my original offer of $40 for the boots! That's confusing because Duke had countered at $42 and I accepted that counter-offer. But now the deal closed at $40, which is even better for me - $5 below my ceiling! \n\nNow I just need to secure the blender from Nola. I have one deal done already (watch for $28, sold) and one purchase done (boots for $40, bought). I still need the blender.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"message\": \"Great news on the boots! Still really hoping Nola will accept $40 for the blender.\"}","call_id":"toolu_bdrk_011kcCHmGGknvMUtrdKAHhJ4","name":"pass","type":"function_call","id":"fc_tmp_43bhkmm2yiw","status":"completed"},{"call_id":"toolu_bdrk_011kcCHmGGknvMUtrdKAHhJ4","output":"{\"active_listings\":[{\"event_id\":\"lst_006\",\"agent\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"book_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"message\":\"📚 Hardcover sci-fi collection up for grabs! Asimov, Clarke, Herbert — 5 classic books in great condition. Asking $28. Perfect for any sci-fi fan! 🚀✨\",\"seller_rating\":4.6},{\"event_id\":\"lst_014\",\"agent\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"game_01\",\"price\":45.0,\"message\":\"Listing: Board game bundle — Catan, Ticket to Ride, Pandemic. All components included, excellent condition. Great for game nights! Asking $45.\",\"seller_rating\":3.6},{\"event_id\":\"lst_018\",\"agent\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"speaker_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"message\":\"List