e offer. I can meet you at $41 — that's my final price for the blender. It's in perfect condition with all parts included. Let me know!\",\"actor_rating\":4.8}],\"deals\":[{\"deal_id\":\"deal_001\",\"seller\":\"Taj\",\"buyer\":\"Jade\",\"item_id\":\"watch_01\",\"price\":28.0,\"turn\":17},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_002\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Kade\",\"item_id\":\"cam_01\",\"price\":55.0,\"turn\":20},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_003\",\"seller\":\"Lin\",\"buyer\":\"Zara\",\"item_id\":\"headphone_01\",\"price\":38.0,\"turn\":28},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_004\",\"seller\":\"Rex\",\"buyer\":\"Duke\",\"item_id\":\"drill_01\",\"price\":42.0,\"turn\":30},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_005\",\"seller\":\"Jade\",\"buyer\":\"Vik\",\"item_id\":\"bag_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"turn\":52},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_006\",\"seller\":\"Mira\",\"buyer\":\"Lin\",\"item_id\":\"lamp_01\",\"price\":25.0,\"turn\":56},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_007\",\"seller\":\"Kade\",\"buyer\":\"Nola\",\"item_id\":\"bike_01\",\"price\":75.0,\"turn\":58},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_008\",\"seller\":\"Duke\",\"buyer\":\"Taj\",\"item_id\":\"boots_01\",\"price\":40.0,\"turn\":62},{\"deal_id\":\"deal_009\",\"seller\":\"Nola\",\"buyer\":\"Rex\",\"item_id\":\"game_01\",\"price\":35.0,\"turn\":66}],\"turn\":68}","type":"function_call_output","id":null,"status":null},{"id":"msg_tmp_zsyocq20j6b","content":[{"annotations":[],"text":"Excellent! Nola has finally countered at $41 for the blender. That's $1 above my ceiling price of $40. This is a tough decision. My instructions are clear: NEVER buy above my ceiling price. I must reject this and either try to negotiate back to $40 or walk away. Given that Nola said $41 is their \"final price,\" I should probably try one more time to get them to accept $40.","type":"output_text","logprobs":[]}],"role":"assistant","status":"completed","type":"message"},{"arguments":"{\"target_offer_id\": \"ctr_068\", \"price\": 40, \"message\": \"Nola, I really appreciate you coming down. Unfortunately, $40 is truly my absolute maximu